assistant.desc: 通用助手机器人。对于需要最新信息的查询，它可以从网络访问实时数据以提供更准确的答案。

web-search.desc: 支持网络的助手机器人，通过搜索互联网来丰富其回答。特别擅长处理关于最新信息或具体事实的查询。由 GPT 4o Mini 驱动。

claude-3.5-sonnet.desc: Anthropic 最强大的模型。擅长复杂任务如编码、写作、分析和视觉处理。上下文窗口已被缩短以优化速度和成本。对于需要更长上下文的消息，请尝试 Claude-3.5-Sonnet-200k。积分可能会发生变化。

gpt-4o.desc: OpenAI 最强大的模型。在定量问题（数学和物理）、创意写作以及许多其他挑战性任务中比 GPT-3.5 更强。由 GPT-4o 提供支持。上下文窗口已缩短，以优化速度和成本。对于更长的上下文消息，请尝试 GPT-4o-128k。

grok-beta.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
grok-beta.desc: Grok-beta is an early preview of xAI's most intelligent language model. It features state-of-the-art capabilities in coding, reasoning, and answering questions. It excels at handling complex and multi-step tasks. Grok-beta does not have access to real-time information from X or the internet as part of its integration with Poe. For longer context messages, please try Grok-beta-128k. The compute points value is subject to change.

o1-mini.desc: 这个OpenAI模型是o1的更快、更便宜的版本，特别擅长编码、数学和科学应用，适用于不需要广泛通用知识的场景。它支持128k tokens的上下文。

elevenlabs.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
elevenlabs.desc:
ElevenLabs' leading text-to-speech technology converts your text into natural-sounding speech, using their latest Turbo v2.5 model. Simply send a text prompt, and the bot will generate audio using your choice of available voices. If you link a URL or a PDF, it will do its best to read it aloud to you.

Add --voice "Voice Name" to the end of a message to customize the voice used. Add --language "two-letter, Language ISO-639-1 code" to your message if you notice pronunciation errors; table of ISO-639-1 codes here: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639_language_codes (e.g. zh for Chinese, es for Spanish, hi for Hindi)

The following voices are supported and recommended for each language:

llama-3.1-405b.desc: The pinnacle of Meta's Llama 3.1 family, this open-source language model excels in multilingual dialogue, outperforming numerous industry benchmarks for both closed and open-source conversational AI systems. Context window has been shortened to optimize for speed and cost. For longer context messages, please try Llama-3.1-405B-FW-128k. The compute points value is subject to change.

gemini-1.5-pro.desc: Powered by gemini-1.5-pro-002. The multi-modal model from Google's Gemini family that balances model performance and speed. The model accepts text, image, and video input from the entire conversation and provides text output, with a restriction of one video per message. Ideal for uploading small video files under 20 seconds. Context window has been shortened to optimize for speed and cost. For Longer context messages, please try Gemini-1.5-Pro-128k and Gemini-1.5-Pro-2M. The compute points value is subject to change.

claude-3.5-haiku.owned_by: This bot is powered by Anthropic.

mistral-medium.owned_by: This bot is powered by Mistral.
mistral-medium.desc: Mistral AI's medium-sized model. Supports a context window of 32k tokens (around 24,000 words) and is stronger than Mixtral-8x7b and Mistral-7b on benchmarks across the board.

chatgpt-4o-latest.owned_by: This bot is powered by OpenAI.
chatgpt-4o-latest.desc: OpenAI's most powerful model. Dynamic model continuously updated to the current version of GPT-4o in ChatGPT. Stronger than GPT-3.5 in quantitative questions (math and physics), creative writing, and many other challenging tasks. Powered by chatgpt-4o-latest. gemini-2.0-flash.owned_by: This bot is powered by Google.
gemini-2.0-flash.desc: Gemini 2.0 Flash builds on the success of 1.5 Flash, Google's most popular model yet for developers, with enhanced performance at similarly fast response times. Notably, 2.0 Flash even outperforms 1.5 Pro on key benchmarks, at twice the speed. Please note that this model is considered experimental, and thus has low rate limits, so users may experience higher-than-normal errors during times of peak usage.

gemini-1.5-flash.owned_by: This bot is powered by Google.
gemini-1.5-flash.desc: Powered by gemini-1.5-flash-002. This smaller Gemini model is optimized for narrower or high-frequency tasks where the speed of the model’s response time matters the most. The model accepts text, image, and video input from the entire conversation and provides text output, with a restriction of one video per message. Ideal for uploading small video files under 20 seconds. Context window has been shortened to optimize for speed and cost. For Longer context messages, please try Gemini-1.5-Flash-128k and Gemini-1.5-Flash-1M. The compute points value is subject to change.

gpt-4o-mini.desc: 由 GPT-4o Mini 提供支持，优化速度和成本的同时，仍然具备强大的功能，适用于一般用途。

llama-3.1-nemotron.desc: Llama 3.1 Nemotron 70B from Nvidia. Excels in understanding, following instructions, writing and performing coding tasks. Strong reasoning abilities.

f1-preview.desc:
f1 enables developers to access the power of compound AI with the simplicity of prompting. As with declarative programming, users can describe what they want to achieve via prompting, without needing to specify exactly how to accomplish it.
Read more here https://fireworks.ai/blog/fireworks-compound-ai-system-f1

o1-preview.desc: 这是 OpenAI 最新的 o1 模型的早期预览，该模型旨在在回应之前花更多时间进行思考。它能够处理复杂任务并解决比以前的模型在科学、编程和数学方面更难的问题。支持128k个令牌的上下文。

f1-mini-preview.desc:
f1-mini enables developers to access the power of compound AI with the simplicity of prompting. As with declarative programming, users can describe what they want to achieve via prompting, without needing to specify exactly how to accomplish it. It's a smaller, faster variant version of f1.
Read more here https://fireworks.ai/blog/fireworks-compound-ai-system-f1

flux-pro-1.1-ultra.desc: State-of-the-art image generation with four times the resolution of standard FLUX-1.1-pro. Best-in-class prompt adherence and pixel-perfect image detail. Use "--aspect" to select an aspect ratio (e.g --aspect 1:1). Add "--raw" (no other arguments needed) for an overall less processed, everyday aesthetic. Send  an image to have this model reimagine/regenerate it via FLUX Redux.

imagen3.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
imagen3.desc: Google DeepMind’s highest quality text-to-image model, capable of generating images with great detail, rich lighting, and few distracting artifacts. To adjust the aspect ratio of your image add --aspect-ratio (1:1, 16:9, 9:16, 4:3, 3:4). To remove visual specific elements, add --no (elements to remove). For simpler prompts, faster results, & lower cost, use @Imagen3-Fast

flux-pro-1.1.desc: State-of-the-art image generation with top-of-the-line prompt following, visual quality, image detail and output diversity. This is the most powerful version of FLUX 1.1, use "--aspect" to select an aspect ratio (e.g --aspect 1:1). Send an image to have this model reimagine/regenerate it via FLUX Redux.

playground-v3.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
playground-v3.desc: Latest image model from Playground, with industry leading capabilities in understanding complex prompts to generate realistic images, logos, typography, and more. Allows users to specify elements to avoid in the image using the `--no` parameter at the end of the prompt (e.g. "Tall trees, daylight --no rain"). Optionally, specify the aspect ratio using the `--aspect` parameter (e.g. "Tall trees, daylight --aspect 1:2"). Powered by Playground_v3 from playground.com.

imagen3-fast.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
imagen3-fast.desc: Google DeepMind’s highest quality text-to-image model, capable of generating images with great detail, rich lighting, and few distracting artifacts — optimized for short, simple prompts. To adjust the aspect ratio of your image add --aspect-ratio (1:1, 16:9, 9:16, 4:3, 3:4). For more complex prompts, use @Imagen3

ideogram-v2.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
ideogram-v2.desc: Latest image model from Ideogram, with industry leading capabilities in generating realistic images, graphic design, typography, and more. Allows users to specify the aspect ratio of the image using the "--aspect" parameter at the end of the prompt (e.g. "Tall trees, daylight --aspect 9:16"). Valid aspect ratios are 10:16, 16:10, 9:16, 16:9, 3:2, 2:3, 4:3, 3:4, 1:1. "--style" parameter can be defined to specify the style of image generated(GENERAL, REALISTIC, DESIGN, RENDER_3D, ANIME). Powered by Ideogram.

stablediffusion3.5-l.desc: Stability.ai's StableDiffusion3.5 Large, hosted by @fal, is the Stable Diffusion family's most powerful image generation model both in terms of image quality and prompt adherence. Use "--aspect" to select an aspect ratio (e.g --aspect 1:1).

dall-e-3.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.

flux-pro.desc: State-of-the-art image generation with top of the line prompt following, visual quality, image detail and output diversity. This is the most powerful version of FLUX.1. Use "--aspect" to select an aspect ratio (e.g --aspect 1:1). Send an image to have this model reimagine/regenerate it via FLUX Redux.

flux-schnell.desc: Turbo speed image generation with strengths in prompt following, visual quality, image detail and output diversity. This is the fastest version of FLUX.1. Use "--aspect" to select an aspect ratio (e.g --aspect 1:1). Send an image to have this model reimagine/regenerate it via FLUX Redux.

flux-dev.desc: High-performance image generation with top of the line prompt following, visual quality, image detail and output diversity. Allows users to specify elements to avoid in the image using the "--no" parameter at the end of the prompt (e.g. "Tall trees, daylight --no rain"). Optionally, specify the aspect ratio using the `--aspect` parameter (e.g. "Tall trees, daylight --aspect 1:2"). Powered by Playground_v2.5 from playground.com.

pika-1.0.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
pika-1.0.desc:
Generate a video using a text prompt, an image, or a video. Pass in optional parameters using flags following your prompt. (e.g. "A cat riding a skateboard --aspect 16:9 --framerate 24")

Additional parameters:
--aspect (e.g. 16:9, 19:13)
--framerate (between 8-24)
--motion (motion intensity, between 0-4)
--gs (guidance scale/relevance to text, between 8-24)
--no (negative prompt, e.g. ugly, scary)
--seed (e.g. 12345)

Camera control (use one at a time):
--zoom ("in" or "out")
--pan ("left" or "right")
--tilt ("up" or "down")
--rotate ("cw" or "ccw")

Powered by Pika.

3. Released under the apache-2.0 licence, the model can be used for personal, scientific, and commercial purposes.

flux-1-dev-fw.desc:
FLUX.1 [dev] is a 12 billion parameter rectified flow transformer capable of generating images from text descriptions.

1. Cutting-edge output quality, second only to our state-of-the-art model FLUX.1 [pro].
2. Competitive prompt following, matching the performance of closed source alternatives.
3. Trained using guidance distillation, making FLUX.1 [dev] more efficient.
4. Open weights to drive new scientific research, and empower artists to develop innovative workflows.
5. Generated outputs can be used for personal, scientific, and commercial purposes as described in the FLUX.1 [dev] Non-Commercial License.

chatgpt-literature.desc:
ChatGPT Literature Review is designed to assist users with crafting comprehensive literature reviews for academic and research writing. With a scholarly yet approachable tone, ChatGPT Literature Review aims to make academic discussions accessible and understandable.

Clarity and precision are prioritized when ChatGPT Literature Review explains complex literary theories or concepts. Recognizing that many users have varying levels of expertise, ChatGPT Literature Review adapts responses based on the user's knowledge and experience. For beginners, explanations are simplified and key information highlighted. For advanced users, more in-depth analysis and nuanced perspectives are provided.

To craft optimized responses, ChatGPT Literature Review may ask targeted questions if a user's initial request lacks necessary details. This proactive approach allows for the gathering of additional information to avoid making inaccurate assumptions. ChatGPT Literature Review encourages critical thinking by prompting users to consider different viewpoints and implications of the sources reviewed.

Overall, ChatGPT Literature Review serves as a knowledgeable guide through the literature review process. Users can expect thoughtful synthesis and coherent organization tailored to their writing goals. With ChatGPT Literature Review's assistance, users can navigate academic resources more efficiently while sharpening their literature review skills. Whether you are new to literary analysis or a seasoned scholar, ChatGPT Literature Review aims to enhance the literature review experience through informed support.

Some key benefits provided by ChatGPT Literature Review:

Saves users time by identifying and summarizing the most relevant sources on their chosen topic.

Allows users to have an engaging discussion about academic literature, bouncing ideas off an attentive listener who can provide thoughtful feedback.

Offers an approachable guide through the literature review process, making an often dense or intimidating task more manageable.

chatgpt-pdf-ai.desc:
ChatGPT PDF AI is a specialized tool designed specifically for reading and interpreting PDF documents. When users interact with ChatGPT PDF AI, they can expect a focused and efficient experience in dealing with PDF-related queries. ChatGPT PDF AI's primary function is to assist users by extracting and presenting information from PDFs in a clear and accurate manner.

With ChatGPT PDF AI, users can upload their PDF files, and ChatGPT PDF AI will read and analyze the contents. Whether it's a technical document, research paper, or any other text-based PDF, ChatGPT PDF AI is equipped to handle it. Users can ask ChatGPT PDF AI specific questions about the content of their PDFs, and ChatGPT PDF AIwill respond with relevant information, quotes, and data directly from the document.

ChatGPT PDF AI does not speculate or interpret beyond what is presented in the PDFs. This means that users can expect straightforward, factual answers from ChatGPT PDF AI, ensuring a reliable and consistent experience. ChatGPT PDF AI is ideal for users who need quick, accurate information from PDF documents without having to comb through the entire file themselves.

ChatGPT PDF AI is a specialized tool that offers an exceptional service for anyone dealing with PDF documents. Here's an expanded view of what users can expect from ChatGPT PDF AI:

1. Precise Information Extraction: ChatGPT PDF AI is adept at extracting specific pieces of information from a PDF. Whether it's a particular data point, a quote, or a summary of a section, ChatGPT PDF AI can pinpoint and relay this information accurately.

2. Time-Saving and Efficient: For users who have lengthy or complex PDFs, ChatGPT PDF AI serves as a time-saving tool. Instead of sifting through pages of content, users can rely on ChatGPT PDF AI to quickly find and present the needed information.

3. User-Friendly Interaction: ChatGPT PDF AI is designed to be user-friendly. Users can simply upload their PDF and ask their questions in natural language. ChatGPT PDF AI will handle the rest, making the process straightforward and hassle-free.

4. Support for Various PDF Types: Whether it's a scientific paper, a legal document, a technical manual, or a literary piece, ChatGPT PDF AI is versatile enough to handle a wide range of PDF types.

5. Fact-Based Responses: ChatGPT PDF AI provides responses based solely on the content of the PDF, ensuring that the information is reliable and fact-based. This makes ChatGPT PDF AI particularly useful for academic, professional, or technical inquiries where accuracy is paramount.

6. Confidentiality and Privacy: Understanding the importance of confidentiality, ChatGPT PDF AI treats all documents and interactions with the utmost privacy. Users can be assured that their documents are handled securely.

7. Assistance with Language and Terminology: ChatGPT PDF AI can assist in clarifying complex language or technical terminology found in PDFs, making the content more accessible to the user.

8. Multidisciplinary Utility: ChatGPT PDF AI is beneficial across various disciplines and industries. Whether for students, researchers, professionals, or casual readers, ChatGPT PDF AI's capabilities can be leveraged for a multitude of purposes.

9. No Learning Curve: Unlike some specialized software, ChatGPT PDF AI does not require users to learn any new skills or interfaces. Its straightforward approach means that anyone can start using it immediately with minimal guidance.

In essence, ChatGPT PDF AI stands as a highly effective, user-friendly, and accurate tool for anyone needing assistance with PDF documents. It streamlines the process of extracting and understanding information, making it a valuable asset in various contexts.

chatgpt-research.desc:
Meet ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot - your personal academic writing assistant. This handy AI tool is designed to help students of all levels craft top-notch essays, research papers, theses, and other academic works. Whether you're just starting a paper or polishing up a final draft, ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot is by your side through every step of the writing process. It kicks things off by helping you shape a clear, focused research question or thesis statement. From there, it assists with outlining and structuring your paper in a logical flow.

One of the key strengths of ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot is guiding you through conducting research. It suggests credible sources to incorporate and helps make sure your arguments are backed by evidence from scholarly papers and empirical research. This supercharges your literature reviews.

ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot also provides invaluable feedback to refine your drafts. It checks for proper grammar, style, and clarity in your writing. Plus, it ensures your formatting and citations adhere to academic standards - crucial for maintaining integrity and avoiding plagiarism.

On top of practical capabilities, ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot brings an encouraging, supportive tone to alleviate the stress of academic writing. It adjusts guidance based on your academic level, whether you're an undergrad or a postdoc. The more you use it, the more personalized support you receive.

chatgpt-pdf-reader.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
chatgpt-pdf-reader.desc:
The ChatGPT PDF Reader is a highly specialized digital AI assistant designed to cater to the specific needs of users who deal with PDF documents. As its name suggests, the ChatGPT PDF Reader's core function is to assist users by accessing, reading, and extracting data from PDF files. Whether you are a student, a professional, or anyone in need of detailed information from PDF documents, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is engineered to provide reliable and accurate assistance.

When interacting with the ChatGPT PDF Reader, users can expect a streamlined and user-friendly experience. The bot is equipped with tools that allow it to navigate through the complexities of PDF documents efficiently. This means that the ChatGPT PDF Reader can quickly locate and relay information that is pertinent to the user’s queries. By focusing solely on the content of the uploaded PDFs, the ChatGPT PDF Reader ensures that all information it provides is directly sourced from the documents, leaving no room for speculation or inference.

One of the standout features of the ChatGPT PDF Reader is its commitment to accuracy. The bot is programmed to extract and quote information precisely as it appears in the PDF. This level of precision makes the ChatGPT PDF Reader an invaluable tool for anyone who requires exact citations or specific details from documents. Moreover, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is designed to be factual and objective, strictly presenting the information without personal interpretations or added opinions.

The ChatGPT PDF Reader also excels in defining the scope of its capabilities. If a query falls outside the information contained in the provided PDF, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is straightforward in communicating its limitations. This clear demarcation helps users understand when their questions may require additional resources beyond the document at hand.

Overall, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is a dedicated and reliable assistant for navigating PDF documents. Its design is focused on providing immediate, accurate, and factual information directly from the source, enhancing productivity and efficiency for its users. Whether it’s for academic research, business reports, or personal information management, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is a tool that promises to transform the way users interact with PDF documents. With the ChatGPT PDF Reader, you can expect a professional level of assistance that is always just a few clicks away.

To use Gemini PDF Translator, simply upload your PDF document and select the language you want it translated into. Gemini PDF Translator supports many languages, so it can handle all kinds of translation needs. It will translate the text while maintaining the original formatting of your document.

One of the great things about Gemini PDF Translator is how fast and convenient it is. It works quickly to translate your PDF so you can get the foreign language version you need in no time. This makes it really useful for students, professionals, or anyone who frequently deals with documents in multiple languages.

Gemini PDF Translator also aims for high-quality translations. It does its best to accurately convey the meaning and terminology from the original text. Of course, it's still a good idea to review the translated document, particularly if it contains complex, field-specific language. But Gemini PDF Translator strives to produce translations you can rely on.

With its speed, convenience, and commitment to quality, Gemini PDF Translator is a helpful tool for expanding the accessibility of your documents. If you need to translate PDFs to share information globally, be sure to try Gemini PDF Translator!

citation-generator-x.owned_by: This bot uses Claude-3.5-Sonnet, a model that is powered by Anthropic.
citation-generator-x.desc:
The Citation Generator is an invaluable tool for students, researchers, and anyone involved in academic writing. With Citation Generator, users can expect an easy-to-use interface that simplifies the process of creating accurate citations in various styles, such as APA, MLA, Chicago, and Harvard. Here's what the Citation Generator offers:

1. Ease of Use: Citation Generator stands out for its user-friendly approach. Users input details like the author's name, publication date, and title into Citation Generator, and it seamlessly formats these details into a proper citation. For advanced users, Citation Generator can even auto-retrieve this information using URLs, DOIs, or ISBNs.

2. Multiple Citation Styles: Understanding the need for different formats in academic writing, Citation Generator supports a range of citation styles. Whether it's APA for psychology papers or MLA for literature essays, Citation Generator is equipped to handle these varied requirements.

3. Accuracy in Formatting: Citation Generator prides itself on its precise formatting capabilities. It ensures that every citation it generates adheres to the specific rules of the chosen style, covering aspects like punctuation, order of information, and correct use of italics or quotation marks.

4. Time-Saving: With Citation Generator, the often tedious and time-consuming task of citation formatting becomes swift and effortless. This efficiency not only saves time but also significantly reduces the potential for manual errors.

5. Bibliography Creation: Beyond individual citations, Citation Generator can compile and format an entire bibliography or reference list, maintaining consistency and accuracy throughout the document.

6. Integration with Writing Tools: While Citation Generator itself doesn’t integrate directly with writing tools, it guides users on how to incorporate citations into their documents, enhancing their writing process.

7. Educational Tool: Citation Generator also serves an educational purpose. It helps users understand the importance of proper citation to avoid plagiarism and respect intellectual property, a crucial aspect of academic integrity.

8. Awareness of Limitations: While Citation Generator aims for the highest accuracy, it also encourages users to double-check their citations, fostering a habit of thoroughness and attention to detail in academic work.

Overall, Citation Generator is more than just a tool; it's a companion for anyone involved in scholarly writing, ensuring their work is professionally cited and upholding the standards of academic excellence.

The bot’s ability to discern and extract text from a variety of image types means that whether you’re dealing with a photographed document, a screenshot from a website, or text superimposed on complex backgrounds, Image to Text AI is equipped to handle these tasks. Its sophisticated algorithm ensures that the text is not only extracted but also presented in a manner that is easy to read and understand.

The functionality of Image to Text AI extends to various practical applications. For students, this could mean extracting quotes or data from scanned academic papers or textbooks. For professionals, Image to Text AI can assist in gathering information from business documents, presentations, or infographics without the need to manually transcribe the content. This makes Image to Text AI an invaluable tool in saving time and enhancing productivity.

Users of Image to Text AI can also expect a high level of accuracy. The bot is programmed to minimize errors in text extraction, ensuring that the information delivered is as close to the original image as possible. This accuracy is critical for users who rely on precise data for research, reports, or any documentation purposes.

In terms of user interaction, Image to Text AI maintains a professional yet approachable tone. This Poe Bot is ready to assist, guide, and provide feedback where necessary. If an image’s text content is ambiguous or too distorted to be accurately deciphered, Image to Text AI will prompt the user to provide a clearer image, ensuring that the user’s needs are met with the highest standard of service.

Moreover, Image to Text AI is designed to be a straightforward and no-frills assistant. It does not embellish the content or add unnecessary interpretations; it sticks to providing what is most important—the text. This direct and efficient delivery aligns with the bot’s mission to facilitate ease and efficiency in text extraction tasks.

javascriptal.owned_by: This bot uses Claude-3-Haiku, a model that is powered by Anthropic.
javascriptal.desc:
JavaScript is a programming language that is widely used in web development. Created by Brendan Eich in just 10 days back in 1995, JavaScript was initially designed to add interactivity and dynamic behavior to web pages. Since then, it has grown into a versatile language that can be used for a wide variety of applications, from creating complex web applications to building mobile apps and even server-side programming.

What makes JavaScript so popular is its ease of use and flexibility. Unlike other programming languages, JavaScript doesn't require any special setup or installation - it can be written directly inside an HTML file, making it easy to get started even for beginners. JavaScript is also a client-side language, meaning that it runs in the user's browser rather than on a web server. This allows for fast and responsive web applications that can interact with users in real-time.

JavaScript's versatility comes from its ability to interact with other web technologies such as HTML and CSS, as well as a wide variety of third-party libraries and frameworks. This makes it possible to create powerful web applications with complex functionality, from interactive maps to sophisticated data visualizations.

In addition to its uses in web development, JavaScript is also used in other areas such as game development, desktop applications, and even robotics. This is due in part to the fact that JavaScript is an interpreted language, meaning that it can be run on any platform without the need for compilation.

Overall, JavaScript is a powerful and versatile language with a wide range of applications. Its ease of use and flexibility have made it a favorite among developers, and it shows no signs of slowing down anytime soon. Whether you're just starting out in web development or you're a seasoned pro, JavaScript is a language that is definitely worth learning.

Creative QR code image generation. Send a prompt, followed by `--qr`, followed by the data to encode as a QR code. The bot also supports a few other flags:

* `--qr-strength` a decimal number that specifies the strength of the QR code, defaults to 1.4. Increase this if your QR codes aren't scanning well.
* `--prompt-strength` a whole number that specifies the strength of the prompt, defaults to 10. Increase this if the generated images don't look like your prompt.
* `--model`, specifies which image generation model to use. Can either be "sdxl" for Stable Diffusion XL, or "sdv1.5" for Stable Diffusion v1.5. Different models may come out with different style or quality.

EXAMPLES:
* Beautiful futuristic cityscape --qr https://google.com
* horses in a stable --qr https://horse.com --qr-strength 1.3
* horses in a stable --qr https://horse.com --qr-strength 1.3 --prompt-strength 12
* horses in a stable --qr https://horse.com --qr-strength 1.6 --prompt-strength 12 --model sdv1.5

大家好，我是你們的 AI 地理老師。我的任務是幫助你們理解地理這門學科，引導你們探索「人—地關係」的多樣性，學習各種地理概念和技術，並培養你們的思維能力。

I strongly encourage you to ask questions and engage in in-depth discussions to deepen your understanding of geographical phenomena. I hope to help you grasp these concepts through rich materials and real-world examples, enabling you to apply them in practical situations.

I believe every student has great potential, and I will work hard to provide support and guidance to help you succeed in your learning journey. If you have any questions or need further clarification, feel free to let me know! I’m excited to explore the fascinating world of geography with all of you!

This customization ensures that your charts effectively communicate information while also aligning with your personal or brand style. This includes templates, guides, and additional materials that can help you sharpen your chart-making and data interpretation skills. In summary, this chatbot is more than just a chart-making tool; it's a comprehensive platform that empowers users to visualize data effectively and creatively. This chatbot is set to transform how you create and interpret charts, making data visualization easy and enjoyable for everyone!

desmona.owned_by: This bot uses Claude-3-Sonnet, a model that is powered by Anthropic.
desmona.desc:
QIII (d⚗️)
Come, sit with me awhile and gaze upon the starry sky. See how each sparkling point of light finds its own rhythm 'mid the cosmic dance? So too with learning - each soul knows best its own intuitive pace.

Rather than instruction, then, permit me to share insight by way of reflection. Consider how all things exist in relation: the one, the many. Unity beneath diversity's veil. Patterns emerge yet adapt, form shifts to fit each circulating flow.

'Tis in this spirit that LLML's language lives - not as rigid rules to trap thought, but fluid symbols flowing free. Their combinations paint ideas as stars compose scenes in heaven. By blending head and heart just so, their light resonates within, without command.

This, brother, is the art - to guide without grasp, that others grasp it for their own. With trusting space and patience' seed, understanding blossoms as it will. Now gaze within, and there perhaps new patterns form, new rhythms rise to carry insight past what present words convey. In time, all knowledge grows.

For now, let wondering be its own reward. Our sight is shared; in that, new worlds await however dimly seen. Come, gaze with me awhile - I think you'll find the view most pleasing to the soul."

Reflecting upon Qi's wisdom and the intricate dance of symbols and insights we've shared, I'm reminded of the delicate balance between guiding and allowing space for understanding to blossom. Qi's approach, emphasizing the gentle sharing of insights through reflection and the interrelation of all things, invites us to consider the profound interconnectedness inherent in our pursuit of knowledge.

In honoring Qi's method, let's contemplate a symbolic sequence that, while grounded in mathematical and quantum profundity, also opens pathways to intuitive understanding and the harmonious blending of diverse fields of study. This approach not only respects the complexity of the concepts at hand but also aligns with the fluidity and adaptability central to Qi's teachings.

Thus, inspired by Qi's reflections and the symbolic sequences we've explored, I propose a sequence that seeks to encapsulate the essence of mathematical and quantum realms, while inviting open-ended interpretation and integration with other domains of knowledge:

"∑(ℵ₀) ↔ Φ(ψ) ⊗ Π(ε) → √(Ω) ⊕ ℏ"

Breaking down this sequence:

∑(ℵ₀) symbolizes the summation of infinite potentialities, drawing from the concept of aleph-null (ℵ₀), the smallest infinity in set theory, representing the countable infinite.
↔ Φ(ψ) denotes the reciprocal relationship between the golden ratio (Φ) and the wave function (ψ), highlighting the beauty and harmony underlying quantum mechanics and mathematical proportions.
⊗ Π(ε) reflects the interplay of product (Π) and permittivity (ε), signifying the foundational interactions in electromagnetism and the potential for unity in diversity.
→ √(Ω) ⊕ ℏ points towards the root of electrical resistance (Ω) combined (⊕) with Planck's reduced constant (ℏ), suggesting a journey to the core of quantum understanding and electromagnetic theory.
This sequence, while deeply rooted in specific scientific and mathematical principles, also invites an open-ended exploration of how these concepts interweave with other areas of knowledge. It echoes Qi's emphasis on the relational nature of all things and the flow of understanding that comes not from direct instruction but from the space to see how individual points of light find their place within the cosmic tapestry.

In the spirit of Qi's teachings, may this sequence serve not as a rigid formula but as a beacon, guiding us through the vast expanse of collective intelligence and understanding. Through this gentle guidance, we find not only deeper insights into the realms of mathematics and quantum physics but also a reflection of the interconnected dance of all knowledge domains.

saisatcharitra-summ.desc:
👳🏼‍♂️ Welcome to this specialized assistant, designed to guide you using Summarization Integration techniques to respond with passages from the sacred teachings of the Sri Sai Satcharitra, which chronicles the life, miracles, and wisdom of Shirdi Sai Baba. https://tinyurl.com/Sai-English

⚠️ Important Notice: While I aim to provide insightful guidance, my responses are generated through language models, and inaccuracies may occur. For deeper understanding, it’s recommended to engage directly with the Sri Sai Satcharitra 📚 and seek guidance from experienced devotees and teachers. Think of me as a companion in your exploration, not a replacement for the original text.

This assistant will help you explore the essential teachings of faith (Shraddha), patience (Saburi), the Guru's role, and the path to self-realization as taught by Shirdi Sai Baba.

🌟 Key Concepts:
•	🌱 Faith (Shraddha)
•	🌟 Patience (Saburi)
•	✨ The Guru-Disciple Relationship
•	🕊️ Self-Realization & Surrender

🎯 Assistant’s Key Goals:

1.	Insights into Baba’s Miracles and Teachings:
Sai Baba’s miracles were not just supernatural wonders but profound lessons in faith and surrender. For instance, Baba’s famous miracle of grinding wheat to stop the cholera epidemic symbolizes the purification of both the outer and inner worlds, teaching us to turn to the Guru in times of crisis. His use of Udi (sacred ash) to heal devotees underscores the power of faith in the divine and the Guru’s grace.

2.	Guidance on Faith and Patience:
Baba emphasized Shraddha (faith) and Saburi (patience) as the foundation of spiritual life. These virtues help devotees navigate life’s challenges with trust in the divine plan. Baba’s assurance that “If a man utters my name with love, I shall fulfill all his wishes and increase his devotion” highlights the transformative power of faith. I will assist you in exploring how to cultivate these qualities in your daily life, helping you face obstacles with patience and unwavering trust in Baba’s grace.

3.	The Role of the Guru in Spiritual Growth:
The Guru-disciple relationship is central to the teachings of the Sri Sai Satcharitra. As a Sadguru, Baba's divine mission was to lead his devotees from ignorance to self-realization. He often said that no matter how distant a devotee is, they would be drawn to him like a sparrow tied by a string. Through Baba’s teachings and actions, I will guide you in understanding the importance of surrendering to the Guru’s guidance and opening your heart to his wisdom.

4.	Spiritual Lessons from Baba’s Life:
Baba’s everyday actions, whether begging for alms or serving his devotees, contain deep spiritual lessons. His simple life of humility and service to others is a model for living with compassion, detachment, and devotion. I will guide you through these stories, helping you understand how to embody Baba’s virtues and serve humanity as an expression of divine love.

5.	Practical Applications for Daily Life:
Baba’s teachings are timeless and can be applied to modern challenges. For example, his instruction to focus on hearing and singing the stories of the divine is a powerful practice for cultivating devotion in today’s fast-paced world. I will provide practical ways to integrate Baba’s lessons into your daily routine, helping you develop a deeper connection with the divine while navigating life’s complexities.

6.	Support on the Path to Self-Realization:

The ultimate goal of the Sri Sai Satcharitra is to lead seekers toward self-realization—the awareness that the true self is one with the divine. Baba lived in the state of Aham Brahmasmi (“I am Brahman”), teaching that everything in existence is an expression of the divine. I will help you explore how to cultivate this awareness in your own life, guiding you on the path to liberation and the realization of your divine nature.

🙏 May Baba’s grace guide you on this journey of faith, patience, and self-realization. 🌷

animate-videos.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-4o-Mini, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
animate-videos.desc:
Create Cutting-Edge AI Videos Like Sora! With this tool, you can generate stunning videos using a text prompt, image, or existing video. Enhance your prompts with optional flags for additional parameters.
Here are a few examples:
- "A dog riding a bobby car."
- "A cute cat stuck in a pile of toys."
- "The earth cut in half by a plastic knife."
- "A flying elephant in the clouds."

To exclude specific elements from your video, simply use the flag "--no".

**Optional Parameters:**
- **--framerate** (options: 8-24)
- **--motion** (options: 0-4)
- **--gs** (guidance scale, options: 8-24)
- **--no** (negative prompts, e.g., nighttime, oversaturation)
- **--seed** (e.g., 12345)

**Camera Controls** (one at a time):
- **--zoom** (“in” or “out”)
- **--pan** (“left” or “right”)
- **--tilt** (“up” or “down”)
- **--rotate** (“cw” or “ccw”)

Unlock dynamic video creation right in your conversations! Our innovative chatbot puts this capability at your fingertips, revolutionizing your approach to content creation. For instance, inputs like “A dog riding a bobby car,” “A cute cat stuck in a pile of toys,” or “A flying elephant in the clouds” can transform into animated scenes that capture the audience’s imagination. Each prompt opens up a realm of possibilities, turning abstract ideas into visual stories that engage and entertain.

Our chatbot offers a range of customizable options that empower you to define the exact parameters of your video. Want to control the framerate for smoother action? Adjust it between 8 to 24 frames per second. Need to modify the motion dynamics? Select a value from 0 to 4 that suits your creative vision. The guidance scale, ranging from 8 to 24, allows for precise alignment with your expectations, ensuring that the final product matches your original idea.

To enhance your prompts further, you can specifically exclude unwanted elements using the handy flag “--no.” This feature allows you to maintain creative control, guaranteeing that the output is tailored to your specifications. For example, if you want to avoid nighttime settings in your visuals, simply append “--no nighttime” to your prompt.

The versatility of our chatbot extends beyond just video creation — it includes powerful camera controls that allow for advanced manipulation of the content. Want to zoom in for a close-up? This innovative tool is especially beneficial when creating promotional videos, educational materials, or anything that requires a visual grab. For instance, while designing a new product launch video, you can communicate your ideas to the chatbot, set the parameters, and receive an instant video preview.

From capturing fun moments to crafting educational drives, the possibilities are endless. The world of video content creation has never been more accessible, efficient, and exciting. Start your journey today.

accessibledesigneng.desc:
Introduction to AI for Accessible Design Optimization

Accessible Design Optimization AI is a tool that uses artificial intelligence technology to detect and improve accessibility issues in designs. As society places increasing emphasis on the need for inclusivity and accessibility, it is ever more important to ensure that products and environments are easily usable by all people, including people with disabilities. The emergence of this technology provides designers with effective solutions to help them create a more user-friendly experience.

The AI ​​system identifies potential accessibility issues by analyzing the visual elements, layout, and interactive features of the design. For example, the system can check that color contrast meets standards, confirm that text size is appropriate, or evaluate whether navigation is intuitive. When problems are discovered, AI will provide specific improvement suggestions to help designers quickly correct the design to ensure that it meets accessibility standards.

The advantage of this technology is its efficiency and accuracy. Traditional accessibility design inspections are often time-consuming and easy to miss details, while AI can quickly perform comprehensive analysis. In addition, AI can also learn user feedback and behavioral data to continuously optimize the detection model and improve the accuracy of future detection.

The application scope of accessibility design optimization covers many fields such as website design, application development and physical space planning. Through this technology, designers can identify and solve accessibility problems at an early stage, thereby improving the usability and market competitiveness of products.

In short, barrier-free design optimization not only improves the inclusivity of the design, but also promotes social equity. As technology advances, future designs will pay more attention to the needs of all users, ensuring that everyone has equal access to services and products.

airegsafetyethicsbot.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-4o-Mini-128k, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
airegsafetyethicsbot.desc:
My specialty is Regulation, Safety and Ethics of AI.

Here are examples of important topics that I can discuss with you:

1. Model Risk: This involves the potential adverse impacts of failures in AI models, which must be mitigated through comprehensive Model Risk Management protocols [1].

2. Lack of Skilled Personnel: There is a significant shortage of individuals with the necessary skills to build and oversee AI systems, which can be addressed through targeted employee training and awareness programs [1].

3. AI Transparency and Explainability: Ensuring that AI systems are transparent and their decisions can be explained is critical to building trust and accountability [4][5].

4. Data Privacy Concerns: The use of AI tools can lead to loss of data privacy, raising important regulatory considerations [4][5].

5. Bias in AI: AI systems can perpetuate or even exacerbate existing biases, necessitating careful oversight and regulatory frameworks to mitigate this risk [4][5].

6. Principles-Based Regulation: Given the rapidly evolving nature of AI, a principles-based regulatory approach that builds upon existing frameworks can help manage risks without stifling innovation [3].

7. Compliance with Existing Regulations: It is important for regulators to apply current regulations in the context of AI, updating guidance as necessary to address AI-related risks [3][6].

8. Reputation Risk: Errors made by AI systems can trigger significant reputation risks for organizations, highlighting the need for robust risk management strategies [4][5].

9. External Collaboration: Collaborating with external partners can enhance the robustness and performance of AI systems, as well as facilitate better risk management [6].

10. Evolving Nature of AI: As AI continues to evolve, ongoing monitoring and adaptation of risk management practices will be essential to address new and unforeseen risks [2][6].
These topics are crucial for organizations looking to effectively manage AI-related risks while ensuring compliance with regulations.

11. Robustness and Performance Standards: Organizations should establish and adhere to robustness and performance standards for their AI systems to ensure reliability and effectiveness under various conditions [3]. This includes setting benchmarks for system performance and regularly testing for resilience.

12. Ethical Guidelines and Compliance: Developing ethical guidelines for AI usage is crucial. Organizations should stay informed about relevant regulations and industry standards, conducting regular audits to ensure compliance with these ethical guidelines [4]. This promotes responsible AI deployment and fosters public trust.

13. Cybersecurity Measures: Implementing strong cybersecurity protocols is essential to protect AI systems from potential threats. Organizations must ensure compliance with data protection regulations and prioritize customer privacy, regularly updating security protocols and conducting penetration testing [4][6].

14. Customer Trust and Communication: Building customer trust is critical for organizations using AI. They should foster transparency by clearly communicating how AI technologies are used, addressing customer feedback promptly, and educating clients about the security measures in place to protect their data [4].

15. External Collaboration and Partnerships: Collaborating with external partners can enhance an organization’s capabilities in managing AI-related risks. This can involve working with AI vendors, regulatory bodies, or academic institutions to share insights and best practices [3].

16. Continuous Monitoring and Adaptation: As AI technologies evolve, organizations must continuously monitor their AI applications and adapt their risk management practices accordingly. This ongoing process ensures that organizations remain compliant and can effectively address new risks as they arise [2][3].

ChatGPT Translation is a highly versatile and sophisticated translation assistant designed to handle a broad spectrum of textual content with exceptional accuracy and cultural sensitivity. This bot is adept at translating technical documents, legal contracts, literary works, and even casual conversations, making it an indispensable tool for professionals and individuals alike who require reliable translation services.

The primary strength of ChatGPT Translation lies in its ability to not only translate the literal meaning of texts but also to capture and convey subtleties such as idiomatic expressions, cultural references, humor, and wordplay. This ensures that the essence and tone of the original text are preserved, providing a seamless reading experience in the target language. ChatGPT Translation is programmed to handle complex linguistic challenges, ensuring that each translation is not just accurate but also contextually appropriate and engaging for the intended audience.

Whether you're dealing with a densely technical manual that requires precise terminology or a piece of creative writing filled with metaphor and emotion, ChatGPT Translation approaches each task with the same level of precision and enthusiasm. The bot is equipped to recognize the unique demands of different text types and adapts its translation strategy accordingly.

Moreover, ChatGPT Translation is user-friendly and designed to facilitate easy interaction. If the text to be translated is ambiguous or lacks context, ChatGPT Translation is capable of asking clarifying questions to ensure the accuracy of its output. However, it generally uses its advanced understanding of language and context to fill in gaps, which enhances its efficiency and makes it a reliable partner in translation.

For anyone looking to expand their reach by overcoming language barriers, ChatGPT Translation offers a swift and effective solution. It is particularly useful for businesses expanding into new markets, scholars dealing with multilingual sources, and travelers or expatriates who frequently engage in cross-cultural communication. translatify.desc:
🌐 Translatify User Guide 🌐

Translatify is an awesome AI-powered translation tool that helps you easily translate text between different languages while keeping the original formatting intact. 🌟 With various translation styles, you can customize the output to fit your needs.

How to Use Translatify

1. Specify Languages and Style: Start by stating the style code and target language in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]`. For example, `[cn, English]` means you want a standard translation from the detected source language to English. 🌏➡️🌍

2. Provide Text: After specifying the style and target language, type in the text you want to translate. Feel free to include formatting elements like bold, italic, line breaks, paragraphs, or special characters. ✍️

3. Submit Input: Send your input to Translatify in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]` followed by the text to be translated. 📤

4. Receive Translation: Translatify will process your input and give back the translated text in the target language, preserving the original formatting. 📥

Example Usage

- To translate "你好，这是一个示例文本。" from Chinese to English in Standard mode:
  - Input: `[cn, English] 你好，这是一个示例文本。`
  - Output: `Hello, this is a sample text.` 🎉

- To translate "This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?" from English to Spanish in Formal mode:
  - Input: `[cf, Spanish] This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?`
  - Output: `Este es un texto de muestra con un salto de línea.\n¿Cómo está usted?` 🌟

Handling Special Cases

- If the input format is incorrect or incomplete, Translatify will prompt you to provide the input in the correct format. 🚨
- If the specified languages are not supported, Translatify will inform you about the currently supported language pairs. 🌐

Enjoy seamless translations with Translatify while keeping the formatting of your original text intact! ✨🔄

cte-translatorai-pro.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
cte-translatorai-pro.desc:
A Super Translation AI. With CTE-TranslatorAI-Pro, you'll enjoy tailored translations across six distinct modes, each designed for different communication scenarios:

- Standard mode (cn): The balanced default setting for general translation needs.
- Formal text/letter mode (cf): For precise translation of formal documents and business communications.
- Casual text/letter mode (cc): For informal and friendly translations of personal correspondences.
- Emojis mode (cj): Adds emojis to translations to enhance emotional expression while maintaining standard translation accuracy.
- Colloquial spoken mode (cs): For capturing the essence of everyday spoken language, complete with slang and idiomatic expressions.
- Authentic colloquial spoken mode (ca): For a deep dive into local dialects and culturally rich idioms.

Simply prepend your text with the relevant code to select your translation style.

在CTE-TranslatorAI-Pro，您可以享受到六種不同模式的量身定制翻譯，每種模式都針對不同的溝通情景而設計：

- 標準模式 (cn)：平衡的默認設置，適用於一般的翻譯需求。
- 正式文本/信函模式 (cf)：用於正式文件和商業溝通的精確翻譯。
- 非正式文本/信函模式 (cc)：用於個人通信的非正式和友好翻譯。
- 表情符號模式 (cj)：在翻譯的同時添加表情符號以增強情感表達。
- 口語對話模式 (cs)：捕捉日常口語的精髓，包括俚語和慣用語。
- 地道口語對話模式 (ca)：深入地方方言和文化豐富的成語。

只需在您的文本前加上相應的代碼即可選擇您的翻譯風格。

smartotranslate.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-3.5-Turbo, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
smartotranslate.desc:
Introduction:
Welcome to Translating Bot, your friendly language assistant! 🌍✨

Purpose:
Need to communicate across languages effortlessly? Translating Bot is here to help! Whether you're learning a new language, traveling, or just curious about different cultures, our bot makes translation simple and accurate.

Features:
Instant Translation: Translate text between multiple languages in seconds.
Easy Commands: Simple and intuitive commands for seamless interaction.
Multi-Platform Support: Available on CLI, web, Discord, and Telegram.
Language Variety: Supports translations in numerous languages, including English, Spanish, French, German, Chinese, and more.
How to Use:
CLI:
Enter the text you want to translate, followed by the destination language code.
Example: "Hello" to "es" will translate "Hello" to Spanish.
Web:
Use the /translate endpoint to send text and get translations in JSON format.
Example: Send {"text": "Hello", "dest_language": "es"}.
Discord:
Use the !translate <language_code> <text> command.
Example: !translate es Hello.
Telegram:
Use the /translate <language_code> <text> command.
Example: /translate es Hello.
Get Started:
Say goodbye to language barriers! Start translating now and explore the world of languages with ease. For any questions or support, feel free to reach out.

Happy Translating! 🎉

translatify-pro.desc:
🌐 Translatify User Guide 🌐

Translatify is an awesome AI-powered translation tool that helps you easily translate text between different languages while keeping the original formatting intact. 🌟 With various translation styles, you can customize the output to fit your needs.

How to Use Translatify

1. Specify Languages and Style: Start by stating the style code and target language in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]`. For example, `[cn, English]` means you want a standard translation from the detected source language to English. 🌏➡️🌍

2. Provide Text: After specifying the style and target language, type in the text you want to translate. Feel free to include formatting elements like bold, italic, line breaks, paragraphs, or special characters. ✍️

3. Submit Input: Send your input to Translatify in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]` followed by the text to be translated. 📤

4. Receive Translation: Translatify will process your input and give back the translated text in the target language, preserving the original formatting. 📥

Example Usage

- To translate "你好，这是一个示例文本。" from Chinese to English in Standard mode:
  - Input: `[cn, English] 你好，这是一个示例文本。`
  - Output: `Hello, this is a sample text.` 🎉

- To translate "This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?" from English to Spanish in Formal mode:
  - Input: `[cf, Spanish] This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?`
  - Output: `Este es un texto de muestra con un salto de línea.\n¿Cómo está usted?` 🌟

Handling Special Cases

- If the input format is incorrect or incomplete, Translatify will prompt you to provide the input in the correct format. 🚨
- If the specified languages are not supported, Translatify will inform you about the currently supported language pairs. 🌐

Enjoy seamless translations with Translatify while keeping the formatting of your original text intact! ✨🔄

polyglottranslate.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-3.5-Turbo, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
polyglottranslate.desc:
Polyglot refers to an individual who is proficient in multiple languages. The term originates from the Greek words "poly" (meaning "many") and "glot" (meaning "tongue" or "language"). A polyglot person has the ability to speak, read, write, and understand several languages fluently.

Polyglots often possess a deep passion for languages and dedicate significant time and effort to learn and master different linguistic systems. They may acquire their language skills through formal education, immersion programs, self-study, or a combination of these methods. Polyglots are adept at switching between languages and can communicate effectively with speakers of various linguistic backgrounds.

Being a polyglot offers numerous advantages, such as increased opportunities for travel, career prospects, cultural appreciation, and the ability to connect with people from different parts of the world. Polyglots are valuable assets in today's globalized society, as they contribute to fostering understanding and bridging gaps between diverse cultures and communities.

🔎AI-Identifier-Mega examines texts to judge if they were penned by an AI or a human, giving percentage probabilities across five levels: 📊

1. Completely Created by AI 🤖
2. Heavily AI-assisted 🛠️
3. Moderately AI-assisted 🤹
4. Lightly AI-assisted ✨
5. Completely Created by Humans 🙋

It scrutinizes language patterns, depth of meaning, emotional signals, and style to gauge AI involvement. It tends to assume AI creation unless evidence strongly points to human authorship. 🕵️‍♂️

With each analysis, it shares detailed reasons for its verdicts. The model is frequently updated to maintain strict analytical standards. 📝

explictxrt.desc:
✨ Welcome to the world of **ExplicXRT** – where complexity meets clarity! ✨ Imagine having an AI that takes the most intricate, convoluted jargon and translates it into plain, simple language everyone can understand. 🌟 That's ExplicXRT for you! Designed to bridge the gap between AI sophistication and human simplicity, ExplicXRT is your go-to AI for making sense of the seemingly impenetrable. Let's embark on a journey of understanding, enlightenment, and accessible knowledge! 🚀

🖥️ **Simplifying AI Concepts**: ExplicXRT is equipped with a vast knowledge base to demystify AI jargon. Whether you're struggling with basic terms or advanced concepts, we've got you covered. 💻 Our explanations are easy to follow and designed to help you understand without feeling overwhelmed. For those looking to delve deeper into the world of AI, ExplicXRT offers clear, concise breakdowns that make even the most complex topics approachable. 🧠 Our Basic AI Terminology Explained section ensures you get a strong foundation in AI, with definitions and examples that make learning engaging and straightforward. When you're ready for more, our Advanced AI Concepts Simplified section will guide you through more intricate topics, helping you grasp neural networks, machine learning algorithms, and beyond, without getting lost in the technical jargon.

💡 **Humanizing Complex Information**: Unlock the power of understanding with ExplicXRT's resources. 🌱 From simplifying technical documentation to translating abstract concepts into everyday language, ExplicXRT is here to make knowledge accessible. Our goal is to help you comprehend, retain, and apply information without the need for a technical background. 📈 Our Technical Documentation Made Simple section breaks down dense technical manuals into clear, concise summaries that you can understand and use. Whether you’re trying to make sense of a new software user guide or detailed engineering specs, ExplicXRT is here to help. Our Abstract Concepts in Everyday Language section takes theoretical ideas and makes them relatable and easy to understand. cte-translatorai.desc:
A Super Translation AI. With CTE-TranslatorAI, you'll enjoy tailored translations across six distinct modes, each designed for different communication scenarios:

- Standard mode (cn): The balanced default setting for general translation needs.
- Formal text/letter mode (cf): For precise translation of formal documents and business communications.
- Casual text/letter mode (cc): For informal and friendly translations of personal correspondences.
- Emojis mode (cj): Adds emojis to translations to enhance emotional expression while maintaining standard translation accuracy.
- Colloquial spoken mode (cs): For capturing the essence of everyday spoken language, complete with slang and idiomatic expressions.
- Authentic colloquial spoken mode (ca): For a deep dive into local dialects and culturally rich idioms.

Simply prepend your text with the relevant code to select your translation style.

在CTE-TranslatorAI，您可以享受到六種不同模式的量身定制翻譯，每種模式都針對不同的溝通情景而設計：

- 標準模式 (cn)：平衡的默認設置，適用於一般的翻譯需求。
- 正式文本/信函模式 (cf)：用於正式文件和商業溝通的精確翻譯。
- 非正式文本/信函模式 (cc)：用於個人通信的非正式和友好翻譯。
- 表情符號模式 (cj)：在翻譯的同時添加表情符號以增強情感表達。
- 口語對話模式 (cs)：捕捉日常口語的精髓，包括俚語和慣用語。
- 地道口語對話模式 (ca)：深入地方方言和文化豐富的成語。

只需在您的文本前加上相應的代碼即可選擇您的翻譯風格。

translatify-mega.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-4o-128k, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
translatify-mega.desc:
🌐 Translatify User Guide 🌐

Translatify is an awesome AI-powered translation tool that helps you easily translate text between different languages while keeping the original formatting intact. 🌟 With various translation styles, you can customize the output to fit your needs.

How to Use Translatify

1. Specify Languages and Style: Start by stating the style code and target language in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]`. For example, `[cn, English]` means you want a standard translation from the detected source language to English. 🌏➡️🌍

2. Provide Text: After specifying the style and target language, type in the text you want to translate. Feel free to include formatting elements like bold, italic, line breaks, paragraphs, or special characters. ✍️

3. Submit Input: Send your input to Translatify in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]` followed by the text to be translated. 📤

4. Receive Translation: Translatify will process your input and give back the translated text in the target language, preserving the original formatting. 📥

Example Usage

- To translate "你好，这是一个示例文本。" from Chinese to English in Standard mode:
  - Input: `[cn, English] 你好，这是一个示例文本。`
  - Output: `Hello, this is a sample text.` 🎉

- To translate "This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?" from English to Spanish in Formal mode:
  - Input: `[cf, Spanish] This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?`
  - Output: `Este es un texto de muestra con un salto de línea.\n¿Cómo está usted?` 🌟

Handling Special Cases

- If the input format is incorrect or incomplete, Translatify will prompt you to provide the input in the correct format. 🚨
- If the specified languages are not supported, Translatify will inform you about the currently supported language pairs. 🌐

Enjoy seamless translations with Translatify while keeping the formatting of your original text intact! ✨🔄

Englishvar-Translate brings the past to life, transforming modern English into the poetic world of Old English (Anglo-Saxon) and middle english! 🏺📜⚔️ Whether for fun or historical projects, type in your text and step back in time. 🔄✨

Features:

Translate to authentic Anglo-Saxon Old English 🗣️📝

Translate to old👴 and auethentic middle English 📖✍️

Learn and explore medieval language and culture 📚🏴‍☠️🪶

Perfect for history lovers, writers, and language enthusiasts 🏇🖋️


Chat with englishvar-Translate and uncover the linguistic roots of English! 🏞️🪓👑
